A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act to provide for the compensation of the chairperson and members of the
2 board of education of Worth County, approved March 12, 1986 (Ga. L. 1986, p. 3710), so
3 as to revise the compensation of such chairperson and board members; to provide for related
4 matters; to provide for an effective date; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 An Act to provide for the compensation of the chairperson and members of the board of
8 education of Worth County, approved March 12, 1986 (Ga. L. 1986, p. 3710), is amended
9 by revising Section 1 as follows:
10 "SECTION 1.
11 The chairperson of the board of education of Worth County shall receive a per diem
12 of $300.00 and each member of the board shall receive a per diem of $200.00 for each day
13 of attendance at meetings of the board or of meeting and traveling inside or outside the
14 state as a member of a committee of the board on official business first authorized by a
15 majority of the board, plus reimbursement for actual expenses necessarily incurred in
