16 connection therewith. The accounts for such service and expenses shall be submitted for
17 approval to the county school superintendent."
18 SECTION 2.
19 This Act shall become effective on the first day of the month following the month in which
20 it is approved by the Governor or in which it becomes law without such approval.
21 SECTION 3.
22 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
